      "content": "i get the coin analogy, but it still feels like there's some weird, invisible thing making it work. like, is there any way people have tried to explain that 'unseen' part? like, for example, are there any theories about hidden variables or some kind of underlying structure that connects them that we just aren't detecting yet?",
